or the television off.

38:55.792 --> 38:58.750
And I'd be cowering in a corner...

39:01.006 --> 39:04.464
...trying to hold my breath
for fear that someone...

39:04.635 --> 39:06.671
...would talk to me.

39:08.597 --> 39:10.462
I was low.

39:12.976 --> 39:14.967
And then one morning, I woke up...

39:15.145 --> 39:18.057
...put on my collar, I got in the car,
and I started driving.

39:18.232 --> 39:20.223
Had no idea where to...

39:20.400 --> 39:23.267
...until I pulled up at this boarded-up church.

39:23.445 --> 39:26.187
This church right next door.

39:26.740 --> 39:30.153
And on the front steps was this...

39:30.619 --> 39:34.828
...beautiful woman clutching
onto a bottle of Captain Morgan.

39:35.040 --> 39:36.996
And She said:

39:38.085 --> 39:39.996
"You the reverend?"

39:40.379 --> 39:43.667
And I said, "I am a reverend."

39:44.132 --> 39:45.713
And She said:

39:45.884 --> 39:47.590
"I've been waiting on you."

39:48.804 --> 39:50.795
Now, folks in this town...

39:50.973 --> 39:53.214
...they say I saved Lettie Mae Thornton.

39:53.433 --> 39:55.719
That without me, She wouldn't be alive.

39:55.894 --> 39:59.432
But what no one seems to understand...

40:00.274 --> 40:05.564
...is that that woman saved me
every bit as much as I saved her.

40:07.573 --> 40:09.188
You done?

40:10.867 --> 40:13.529
-Sorry.
-You have nothing to apologize for...

40:13.745 --> 40:16.578
...so stop apologizing.

40:17.207 --> 40:18.993
Okay.

40:19.793 --> 40:22.660
You know that there's no liquor
in this house.

40:23.088 --> 40:24.373
Yes.

40:24.590 --> 40:27.332
Well, that's because my wife
is a good person...

40:27.551 --> 40:29.633
...a deeply good person.

40:29.803 --> 40:32.886
But she's got a disease.

40:33.098 --> 40:35.714
It's a disease that don't discriminate.

40:35.934 --> 40:37.925
It's like a rat. It'll eat whatever.

40:38.145 --> 40:42.354
Booze, pills, gambling, sex...

40:43.400 --> 40:45.391
...Or vampire blood.

40:48.405 --> 40:50.646
You're a nice girl, Willa.

40:50.866 --> 40:53.357
And I read about what you've
been through in that book.

40:53.577 --> 40:56.910
And I am so very sorry for it.

40:57.789 --> 41:01.828
But to Lettie Mae, all you look like now
is a bottle of Captain Morgan.

41:02.044 --> 41:04.751
I can't have you around here no more.

41:05.505 --> 41:07.757
She manipulated you once
and she'll do it again.

41:10.052 --> 41:11.588
Okay, I understand.

41:14.640 --> 41:17.177
-WhO's gonna protect you?
-God will, darling.

41:18.310 --> 41:19.846
Just like he always has.

41:20.812 --> 41:22.768
Good luck.

41:28.320 --> 41:31.812
Thank you, Willa Burrell,
for everything you've done.

41:32.032 --> 41:35.115
But I rescind your invitation
from this house.

41:41.625 --> 41:43.581
[MOANS]

41:44.628 --> 41:46.584
Hey, man.

41:54.137 --> 41:55.923
Lafayette?

41:57.724 --> 41:59.555
Lafayette, come on.

41:59.768 --> 42:01.633
Lafayette, come on. Wake up, man.

42:01.853 --> 42:03.104
Lafayette, wake up.

42:03.271 --> 42:05.683
What the hell is your malfunction?

42:05.899 --> 42:08.390
-I thought you OD'd on me.
-Never.

42:08.610 --> 42:11.898
I told you, I is a professional.

42:15.033 --> 42:17.115
Lookie at you.

42:17.327 --> 42:19.659
You worried about me?

42:20.372 --> 42:21.737
Am I growing on you?

42:22.624 --> 42:24.034
Oh, Shut up.

42:24.251 --> 42:25.787
-It's cute.
-Stop.

42:26.002 --> 42:27.867
It is.

42:28.672 --> 42:31.880
Let me fix your neck, and then I have to go.

42:32.092 --> 42:35.209
Okay, I'm stopping.

42:52.988 --> 42:55.320
-IS you--?
-What?

42:55.782 --> 42:57.693
Grooving on me?

43:03.165 --> 43:07.078
-Look, |--
-I'm sorry. I must've misread you or something.

43:07.294 --> 43:11.003
No, no, you didn't misread anything.

43:11.214 --> 43:13.045
It's just...

43:14.009 --> 43:16.921
...you know, I'm with Jessica.

43:18.430 --> 43:20.045
All right.

43:21.141 --> 43:22.802
I gets it.

43:27.397 --> 43:28.807
Good night.

43:29.024 --> 43:31.060
Nighty-night, lover.

43:46.500 --> 43:48.491
[MOANING]

44:19.032 --> 44:21.023
[BOTH MOANING AND GRUNTING]

44:25.956 --> 44:27.662
PAM:
Eric?

44:27.874 --> 44:31.742
Jesus fucking Christ, Pam.

44:34.172 --> 44:37.710
-Now what?
-I wouldn't, Mr. Northman.

44:37.926 --> 44:40.542
You're more outnumbered
than you're aware.

44:42.055 --> 44:43.090
[GROWLING]

44:45.725 --> 44:48.216
What's your name, girl?

44:48.436 --> 44:50.051
Eric? I don't understand?

44:50.897 --> 44:51.807
[IN FRENCH]

44:52.023 --> 44:53.308
Everything's going to be fine.

44:53.733 --> 44:55.394
It's a threat, that's all.

44:56.027 --> 44:57.403
If they were going to kill us...

44:58.113 --> 44:59.603
...they would have done it already.

45:01.032 --> 45:02.363
Tell him your name.

45:03.034 --> 45:04.695
Sylvie.

45:05.036 --> 45:06.071
My name is Sylvie.

45:06.288 --> 45:11.954
Mm. Sylvie. So very pretty.

45:12.460 --> 45:13.210
[IN JAPANESE]

45:13.420 --> 45:14.660
Take her.

45:14.880 --> 45:16.165
[IN ENGLISH]
Mr. Northman.

45:16.381 --> 45:17.917
[PAM GASPS]

45:20.051 --> 45:21.166
[WHIMPERING]

45:21.344 --> 45:23.050
Eric!

45:25.640 --> 45:26.891
[IN ENGLISH]
Who sent you?

45:27.058 --> 45:30.095
We are here
at the Yakonomo Corporation's behest.

45:34.190 --> 45:36.806
Well, then, tell them I understand.

45:36.985 --> 45:38.850
They made their point.

45:39.404 --> 45:42.942
I will be more careful in the future, I promise.

45:43.575 --> 45:46.942
You have a choice to make, Mr. Northman.

45:47.370 --> 45:49.827
One of them has to die.

45:51.207 --> 45:52.913
You pick.

45:54.628 --> 45:55.743
No.

45:56.338 --> 45:57.623
Do it.

45:57.839 --> 45:59.704
-Stop! Stop!
SYLVIE: Eric!

46:00.926 --> 46:02.666
Okay, what do you want?

46:03.595 --> 46:06.632
Money? I got money.

46:07.182 --> 46:11.391
What are they paying you? I'll double it.
I will triple it for you.

46:12.062 --> 46:13.848
You're a wealthy man...

46:14.064 --> 46:16.476
...but you are no corporation.

46:16.691 --> 46:18.352
Choose.

46:18.568 --> 46:20.433
I'm so sorry, Eric.

46:23.907 --> 46:25.317
Me.

46:25.533 --> 46:26.943
No.

46:27.452 --> 46:28.817
Kill me.

46:29.037 --> 46:33.030
The Authority wants you alive, I'm afraid.

46:44.970 --> 46:46.585
Pam.

46:50.892 --> 46:51.927
Pam lives.

46:56.398 --> 46:58.013
[SYLVIE GASPS]

47:11.037 --> 47:11.822
[IN JAPANESE]

47:11.997 --> 47:12.986
Let's go.

47:13.665 --> 47:15.326
The sun'll be coming up soon.

47:15.542 --> 47:17.749
[GRUNTING]

47:19.754 --> 47:22.211
Did you contract the virus on purpose?

47:22.382 --> 47:24.668
On purpose, no.

47:25.593 --> 47:29.632
But did I go about my dealings
with a devil-may-care attitude?

47:30.265 --> 47:31.801
Absolutely.

47:37.063 --> 47:39.554
You can't give up, Eric.

47:39.774 --> 47:41.105
With an ample blood supply...

47:41.317 --> 47:44.309
...vampires are living longer
and longer with this disease.

47:44.529 --> 47:47.566
And who knows? They're working on a cure.

47:47.782 --> 47:49.738
They could have one soon.

47:50.452 --> 47:52.613
Please.

47:52.829 --> 47:55.445
I will help keep you well until--

47:55.665 --> 47:57.326
Why?

47:58.793 --> 48:01.956
Do you regret the choice
you made that night?

48:02.172 --> 48:04.163
I made the only choice I could.

48:04.382 --> 48:06.714
Then don't make me watch this.

48:06.926 --> 48:09.417
-Don't make me watch...
-I released you some time ago.

48:09.637 --> 48:12.014
-...aS you had to watch Nora.
-You're free to leave.

48:12.182 --> 48:13.467
Do not do this to me.

48:16.186 --> 48:18.177
Goddamn you.

48:21.775 --> 48:25.063
For more than a thousand years,
the world has been my oyster.

48:25.779 --> 48:28.816
And it still can be.

48:29.240 --> 48:31.697
I'll do anything.

48:32.494 --> 48:34.780
I've lost my taste for oysters, Pam.

48:35.371 --> 48:36.872
No.

48:39.709 --> 48:41.210
You Should go.

48:42.837 --> 48:44.828
[SOBBING]

49:01.064 --> 49:03.680
Sarah Newlin.

49:03.900 --> 49:05.561
What about her?

49:05.777 --> 49:09.440
What if I told you
Jason Stackhouse let her live?

49:12.742 --> 49:15.358
-He didn't.
-He did.

49:15.578 --> 49:17.284
And She's out there.

49:17.497 --> 49:19.408
-Where?
-No one's seen her.

49:19.958 --> 49:22.495
I have to imagine she's in hiding somewhere.

49:26.047 --> 49:27.457
[INHALES DEEPLY]

49:29.801 --> 49:31.166
[G RU NTS]

49:41.521 --> 49:44.137
Well, let's go find her.

49:44.357 --> 49:46.097
Shall we?

49:47.986 --> 49:49.977
[MOANING]

49:57.829 --> 50:00.286
Hold your breath with me, Noomi.

50:01.416 --> 50:03.452
We breathe together...

50:03.668 --> 50:06.000
...we climax together.

50:06.379 --> 50:07.710
[BOTH INHALE DEEPLY]

50:13.178 --> 50:15.715
[BOTH GRUNT]

50:15.930 --> 50:17.181
Namaste.

50:21.853 --> 50:23.764
[BOTH SIGH]

50:31.821 --> 50:35.234
Oh, Noomi, Noomi, Noomi.

50:35.450 --> 50:39.989
Sanbir, Sanbir, Sanbir.

50:41.789 --> 50:44.656
I have made it my life's work...

50:44.876 --> 50:48.118
...to steer lost souls onto the path.

50:48.338 --> 50:50.420
Not once did it occur to me...

50:50.632 --> 50:53.214
...that along would come a student...

50:54.552 --> 50:57.794
...who could so wholly...

50:58.014 --> 51:01.802
...and completely set me free.

51:02.727 --> 51:05.935
You make me whole and free too, guru.

51:07.106 --> 51:11.566
I walked into this institute five months ago...

51:11.778 --> 51:15.487
...a clueless Christian woman...

51:15.823 --> 51:17.984
...named Noomi...

51:19.160 --> 51:23.403
...who believed that life on Earth
was just an audition to get into heaven.

51:23.915 --> 51:27.874
I never knew that life on Earth
could be heaven.

51:29.379 --> 51:31.415
There is no heaven, Noomi.

51:32.298 --> 51:35.790
There is only the now.

51:36.636 --> 51:38.752
And now, be a doll...

51:38.930 --> 51:42.673
...and go pick out a nice bottle
Of red from the cellar...

51:42.892 --> 51:47.431
...while I draw us an Ayurvedic
foaming bath, will you?

51:47.772 --> 51:49.763
Yes, guru.

52:14.549 --> 52:15.959
[SIGHS]

52:23.725 --> 52:25.135
Oh.

52:35.111 --> 52:37.523
[GASPS THEN GRUNTS]

52:38.072 --> 52:39.687
Who are you?

52:40.199 --> 52:42.155
What do you want?

52:44.912 --> 52:47.073
HIROKI:
Do you know this woman?

52:47.290 --> 52:49.201
Her name is Sarah Newlin.

52:49.375 --> 52:51.832
We have reason to believe She is here.

52:54.172 --> 52:56.288
I cannot tell a lie.

52:56.466 --> 52:59.674
Yes, I know her.

53:01.554 --> 53:03.010
Where is She?

53:05.933 --> 53:08.925
This I will not tell you.

53:10.146 --> 53:12.762
How very unhelpful of you.

53:15.610 --> 53:16.395
[IN JAPANESE]

53:16.611 --> 53:17.851
Do it.

53:18.071 --> 53:19.982
[FLESH SQUELCHES]

53:20.156 --> 53:22.442
HIROKI:
Sarah Newlin!

53:22.658 --> 53:24.649
[PANTING]

53:37.256 --> 53:38.245
[SNIFFS]

53:38.424 --> 53:40.415
Sookie, human.

53:42.595 --> 53:45.257
-Oh, my God, Holly.
-Hey there.

53:45.473 --> 53:47.009
Oh, my God.

53:47.892 --> 53:50.304
-Where have you been?
-I don't know.

53:51.521 --> 53:54.228
-Sookie!
SOOKIE: Bill!

53:57.485 --> 53:59.021
We got the girl! Take him out!

53:59.362 --> 54:01.978
[GROWLING]

54:02.740 --> 54:04.025
Fuck you!

54:04.700 --> 54:06.315
[SCREAMING]

54:15.211 --> 54:17.918
ANDY: That all of them?
JASON: I think so.

54:18.131 --> 54:19.996
What the fuck were you thinking, Sookie?

54:20.216 --> 54:22.923
Don't answer me.
Do not fucking talk, all right?

54:23.136 --> 54:24.467
You swallow any blood?

54:24.637 --> 54:28.505
What about your eyes? Get any in your eyes?
Just shake your head yes or no.

54:29.183 --> 54:31.344
Fuck! Help me wash her Off in the river.

54:31.561 --> 54:34.348
-I'm on it.
-And you.

54:34.522 --> 54:36.012
What the fuck were you thinking, huh?

54:36.190 --> 54:39.808
Tell me I ain't good enough to protect her,
and this is what you come up with?

54:39.986 --> 54:41.942
It was her idea, Alcide.

54:42.113 --> 54:44.399
I've known her long enough
not to change her mind.

54:44.574 --> 54:47.441
Yeah, go on, tell me about Sookie
like I don't know her...

54:47.660 --> 54:49.651
...and I swear to God, I will fucking kill you.

54:49.829 --> 54:51.114
[GUNSHOT]

54:51.289 --> 54:52.324
Alcide!

54:53.499 --> 54:54.955
[GUNSHOT]

54:55.334 --> 54:56.323
[GUNSHOT]

54:56.502 --> 54:58.663
Andy, behind the tree.

55:02.467 --> 55:04.332
[MEN GRUNT]

55:05.636 --> 55:09.549
Alcide! Alcide! Alcide!

55:11.225 --> 55:13.477
No,no,no!

55:14.228 --> 55:15.263
IS he breathing?

55:16.189 --> 55:20.148
I could-- Or one of us could turn him for you,
but we would have to do it--

55:20.318 --> 55:21.683
SOOKIE:
No.

55:23.446 --> 55:24.652
You sure, Sook?

55:25.490 --> 55:28.277
I've been down that road before.

55:34.332 --> 55:36.323
[SOBBING]

55:48.304 --> 55:49.919
Ambulance.

55:50.806 --> 55:53.218
You pulled the trigger, Lou.

55:55.144 --> 55:58.227
I told you life wasn't gonna be the same.

56:03.945 --> 56:05.936
[SOBBING]
